{"title":"山乡邮递员","authors":["沈前祥"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":4,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山乡邮递员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沈前祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭两只脚踩动自行车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踩天涯成为咫尺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后轮追赶前轮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成月亮和太阳的关系"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜与白天旋转"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旋转你为晨报、晚报、日报"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用邮路捆住大山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难怪山拒绝不了日月覆盖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你将邮路甩过江河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涉激流你把自己当成桥梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车轮很圆，你送书信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使好多家人团圆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是亲人，走向了所有人家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路程再长不及你情长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听车铃声不断响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就有了与亲人对话声……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难怪你总愿意早出晚归"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是太阳月亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轮番在山乡明亮出现……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}